Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.25,0:02:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[...小猫的摇篮曲.]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.76,0:02:17.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连自己都管不好的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.56,0:02:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然还想照顾小猫 真是笑死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.10,0:02:23.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 又不能就那样放着不管
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.04,0:02:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次又捡来别人扔的猫了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.29,0:02:34.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 它的主人好像不能再养它了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.44,0:02:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.83,0:02:40.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不打算照顾到底的话就别抱回来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.23,0:02:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好坏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.32,0:02:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的很好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.51,0:02:50.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?小猫?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.40,0:02:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎 怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.45,0:02:55.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是肚子饿了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.50,0:03:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千帆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.95,0:03:04.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第五题的答案是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.86,0:03:07.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?千世也不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.36,0:03:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.44,0:03:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.09,0:03:16.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.71,0:03:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.54,0:03:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子饿了!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.94,0:03:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在妈妈出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.31,0:03:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有这些了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.11,0:03:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不是要这种零食...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.76,0:03:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.81,0:03:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是我饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.57,0:03:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这只小猫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.98,0:03:39.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.34,0:03:40.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.81,0:03:43.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前的主人好像不能继续养它了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.10,0:03:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以想问问能不能分些食物给它
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.94,0:03:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘘
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.36,0:03:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.95,0:03:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以去小鸠的房间吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.72,0:03:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.43,0:03:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝得真香啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.25,0:04:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.71,0:04:02.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.76,0:04:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们为什么要用那么小的声音说话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.56,0:04:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.03,0:04:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.57,0:04:14.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这间公寓是禁止养宠物的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.89,0:04:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前住在这里的人曾经养过狗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.37,0:04:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邻居都抱怨叫声太吵了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.87,0:04:25.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以妈妈说带着宠物的入住者就推掉好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.37,0:04:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那...这么说不能在这里养它了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.38,0:04:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再去拜托它以前的主人看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.92,0:04:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道谁是它的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.34,0:04:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小猫是放在一个箱子里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.72,0:04:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上边也没有写主人的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.01,0:04:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.73,0:04:47.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这样的话小猫就要孤身一人了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.41,0:04:51.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能找到愿意收养它的人就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.59,0:04:53.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.00,0:04:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明天到艾草保育园拜托清花老师看看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.08,0:04:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.31,0:05:02.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清花阿姨的话一定会同意的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.35,0:05:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果养在艾草保育园 我们随时可以去看它
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.80,0:05:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即然这样就得取个名字了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.75,0:05:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠 叫什么好?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.56,0:05:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?问我吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.37,0:05:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.55,0:05:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问得太突然了想不出来!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.53,0:05:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它长得这么白 叫牛奶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.11,0:05:26.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且它好像很喜欢牛奶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.47,0:05:27.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牛奶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.98,0:05:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱的名字 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.30,0:05:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.23,0:05:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.07,0:05:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浑身雪白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.51,0:05:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它叫牛奶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.61,0:05:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牛奶 过来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.32,0:05:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要抱抱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.27,0:05:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.56,0:05:46.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我摸摸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.42,0:05:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好像都很高兴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.47,0:05:51.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可以在这里养吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.89,0:05:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让君 你来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.35,0:06:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.07,0:06:06.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让 你是不是有猫过敏症
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.74,0:06:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫...过敏?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.19,0:06:11.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这样打嚏喷或者起湿疹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.02,0:06:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,严重的时候还会引起哮喘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.83,0:06:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清花老师 保育园里是不能养猫的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.29,0:06:24.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.59,0:06:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠 对不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.96,0:06:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这样的心血来潮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.97,0:06:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后只能是给大家添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.66,0:06:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么是心血来潮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.10,0:06:36.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你能负责到底吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.31,0:06:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤本君
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.69,0:06:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果只是为了自我满足才抱回来看看的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.35,0:06:42.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和抛弃他的人同罪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.69,0:06:49.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.58,0:06:51.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经不要紧了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.88,0:06:54.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才是 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.32,0:07:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 住手啊 别粘着我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.92,0:07:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我虽然是布偶但又不是布偶啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.22,0:07:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠 你在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.41,0:07:15.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清花老师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.68,0:07:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐在你旁边可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.60,0:07:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.43,0:07:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你失望了真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.64,0:07:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那回事 我才应该道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.13,0:07:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤本君他也没有什么恶意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.18,0:07:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能在某种意义上...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.71,0:07:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那只小猫身上看到了自己的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.51,0:07:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.68,0:07:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.93,0:07:44.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿意收养小猫的人 我也帮忙找找看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.39,0:07:47.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 一定找得到的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.56,0:07:49.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.94,0:07:52.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 接下来你打算怎么做?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.40,0:07:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寻找愿意收养牛奶的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.74,0:07:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能给大家造成困扰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.62,0:08:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赞成 我可是相当的困扰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.90,0:08:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.82,0:08:09.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清花阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.63,0:08:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.85,0:08:12.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牛奶在吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.22,0:08:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫过敏症?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.90,0:08:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样 真是对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.49,0:08:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.73,0:08:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是拜托妈妈看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.84,0:08:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以啊 规定禁止饲养宠物的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.58,0:08:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说了的话会让妈妈为难的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.98,0:08:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.03,0:08:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有哪位好心人愿意收养这只小猫的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.62,0:08:41.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请成为这只小猫的主人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.21,0:08:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请照顾这只小猫...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.27,0:08:47.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.70,0:08:50.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千帆 千世
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.97,0:08:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牛奶 到这里来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.85,0:08:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有乖乖听话吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.60,0:08:58.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 虽然拜托过清花老师了但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.14,0:09:01.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也去了保育园一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.50,0:09:02.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.74,0:09:04.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是小鸠的错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.94,0:09:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 还没有找到愿意收养的好心人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.04,0:09:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也一起帮忙找
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.98,0:09:14.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牛奶 我们一定帮你找到愿意收养你的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.82,0:09:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真对不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.21,0:09:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家里光照顾小孩子就够呛了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.05,0:09:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦 凯瑟琳你怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.36,0:09:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.66,0:09:32.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.32,0:09:38.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有完没完啊!你们这些推销员!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.45,0:09:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.82,0:09:42.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牛奶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.01,0:09:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 堂元先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.69,0:09:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.86,0:10:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牛奶 过来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.74,0:10:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好厉害好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.97,0:10:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找愿意收养那只小猫的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.11,0:10:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认识的都是些独居的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.28,0:10:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然一下子想不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.01,0:10:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过会帮你找找看的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.70,0:10:27.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.37,0:10:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我老是给大家添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.95,0:10:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不当这是麻烦哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.19,0:10:35.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠那么执着认真
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.33,0:10:37.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都会愿意帮你的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.80,0:10:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.06,0:10:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过还是别再去打扰陌生人家了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.88,0:10:45.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 藤本先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.05,0:10:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是为了自我满足才抱回来看看而已的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.97,0:10:50.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和抛弃它的人没什么两样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.86,0:10:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是老样子呢 清和
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.69,0:10:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别太把他的话当真哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.18,0:11:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想不会有人愿意抛弃那么可爱的小猫的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.18,0:11:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是有什么苦衷的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.04,0:11:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那时的藤本先生...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.55,0:11:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去非常寂寞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.94,0:11:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如藤本先生所说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.71,0:11:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能半途而废
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.57,0:11:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能做到的一定要尽力去做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.06,0:11:22.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这次我去找认识的人家问问看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.96,0:11:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 有什么事的话 就打我的手机吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.80,0:11:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.81,0:11:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.08,0:11:42.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像不在家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.55,0:11:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休业中呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.56,0:11:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.24,0:12:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...我家是开食品店的 养猫有点不好...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.58,0:12:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.55,0:12:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮不上忙 不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.88,0:12:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好 我是三原
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.69,0:12:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清花?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.16,0:12:22.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?小猫?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.25,0:12:25.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来要是能养在这里就没事了...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.68,0:12:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们是去为小猫找主人了啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.43,0:12:33.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我知道了 再见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.50,0:12:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.83,0:12:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.25,0:12:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天已经全黑了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.52,0:12:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牛奶也累了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.33,0:12:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牛奶?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.53,0:13:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 它肚子饿了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.05,0:13:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一 二
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.59,0:13:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.87,0:13:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都做不了 真是太没用了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.02,0:13:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连猫粮都买不起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.71,0:13:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.26,0:13:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 千世
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.58,0:13:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.63,0:13:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是拜托妈妈看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.36,0:13:31.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 妈妈的话 肯定会允许的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.49,0:13:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话今天就和牛奶一起睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.06,0:13:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 一起睡 小鸠也来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.55,0:13:37.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.18,0:13:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那个时候的...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.06,0:13:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦 歌唱得很好的小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.70,0:13:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠 是你认识的人?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.09,0:13:49.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 小宝宝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.31,0:13:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天工休 所以他妈妈在照看他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.75,0:13:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.39,0:13:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 可是为什么您会在这里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.22,0:14:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说这里有一个找人收养小猫的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.56,0:14:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.31,0:14:10.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦啊啦 是这小家伙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.18,0:14:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是又小又可爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.74,0:14:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果可以的话 能不能让我家收养它呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.97,0:14:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.61,0:14:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 孙子是独生子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.04,0:14:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有小猫一起玩的话...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.28,0:14:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 可是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.31,0:14:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有的人碰到猫就会打喷嚏 小宝宝没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.65,0:14:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个披萨店员也在担心同样的问题呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.47,0:14:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,披萨店员?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.74,0:14:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 送货的时候挨家在问能不能收养小猫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.84,0:14:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我路过的时候听到了以后 就到这里来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.98,0:14:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是藤本先生...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.92,0:14:58.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家孙子非常喜欢动物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.14,0:15:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没有猫过敏症
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.75,0:15:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦啊啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.80,0:15:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了呢 牛奶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.56,0:15:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不再是孤零零一个人了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.48,0:15:14.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.70,0:15:15.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜 牛奶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.42,0:15:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还会去看你的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.24,0:15:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 等等 老奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.05,0:15:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是牛奶的饭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.22,0:15:26.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.00,0:15:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牛奶就拜托您了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.17,0:15:33.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.17,0:15:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牛奶一不在了 感觉房间好像变大了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.61,0:15:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 舒服多了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.72,0:15:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.91,0:15:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牛奶的牛奶盘子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.46,0:16:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千帆和千世一定也是同样的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.59,0:16:03.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.90,0:16:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.50,0:16:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.92,0:16:13.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.25,0:16:15.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.88,0:16:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.85,0:16:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要找千帆和千世的话 她们在屋顶上哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.47,0:16:30.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家人会不会疼牛奶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.64,0:16:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个看起来很慈祥的老奶奶呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.71,0:16:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位老奶奶的话一定会的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.15,0:16:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.96,0:16:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那是...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.40,0:16:44.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘记还给你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.49,0:16:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牛奶的...牛奶盘子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.33,0:16:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.23,0:16:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.62,0:16:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认识那位老奶奶时候也是这样一个满月之夜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.24,0:17:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樱花盛开得很美丽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.34,0:17:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老奶奶带出来散步的小宝宝哭个不停
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.82,0:17:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我试着哄了哄小宝宝...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.13,0:17:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是越哄他哭得越厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.99,0:17:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.86,0:17:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后来呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.35,0:17:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后...我唱了首歌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.18,0:17:27.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?小鸠唱歌了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.28,0:17:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 然后小宝宝就不哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.42,0:17:34.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是首什么样的歌?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.27,0:17:37.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.63,0:17:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想听
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.22,0:17:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.64,0:17:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唱来听听 小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.69,0:17:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.14,0:17:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.62,0:18:07.27,XXX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(300,300)}春に咲く花
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.62,0:18:07.27,XXX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(300,300)}春天绽放的鲜花
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.72,0:18:13.92,XXX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(300,300)}夏広がる空よ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.72,0:18:13.92,XXX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(300,300)}夏天宽广的天空哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.49,0:18:26.87,XXX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(300,300)}心の中に刻まれて煌めく
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.49,0:18:26.87,XXX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(300,300)}在心中闪闪发光
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.26,0:18:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这首歌是...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.82,0:18:40.01,XXX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(300,300)}朝に降る雨 窓を閉ざす日にも
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.82,0:18:40.01,XXX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(300,300)}哪怕清晨下起雨 关起窗户的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.51,0:18:53.16,XXX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(300,300)}胸にあふれる光は雲の上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.51,0:18:53.16,XXX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(300,300)}充满胸中的光在云层之上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.04,0:19:07.61,XXX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(300,300)}私を導く遠い遠い呼び声よ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.04,0:19:07.61,XXX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(300,300)}引导我的遥远的声音啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.95,0:19:20.45,XXX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(300,300)}微笑むように 歌うように 響く風の音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.95,0:19:20.45,XXX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(300,300)}好像在微笑好像在歌唱一样的风声
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.82,0:19:27.45,XXX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(300,300)}喜び悲しみ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.82,0:19:27.45,XXX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(300,300)}喜悦与悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.74,0:19:33.85,XXX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(300,300)}すべて抱いて歩いてる
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.74,0:19:33.85,XXX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(300,300)}全部包容一同前行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.18,0:19:40.96,XXX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(300,300)}私の手と君の手を
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.18,0:19:40.96,XXX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(300,300)}把我和你的手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.21,0:19:47.04,XXX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(300,300)}強く繋ぐもの
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.21,0:19:47.04,XXX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(300,300)}紧紧连在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.72,0:20:08.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.75,0:20:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.29,0:20:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牛奶的事...谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.85,0:20:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个很好的人收养了它
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.53,0:20:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这都多亏了藤本先生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.42,0:20:37.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这事吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.20,0:20:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.79,0:20:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.63,0:20:48.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想到了件很重要的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.57,0:20:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能借电话给我用呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.69,0:20:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 如果知道有谁喜欢猫的话就联络我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.10,0:20:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.56,0:21:01.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清和?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.74,0:21:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.62,0:21:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那...那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.00,0:21:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.20,0:21:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.13,0:21:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 找到愿意收养小猫的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.25,0:21:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是想告诉你这个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.68,0:21:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.51,0:21:22.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 是藤本先生找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.77,0:21:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清和?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.07,0:21:27.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.55,0:21:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你费了不少心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.95,0:21:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.78,0:21:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就这样...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.19,0:21:42.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,增加了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.73,0:21:44.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...为什么呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.54,0:21:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明找到牛奶的新主人是藤本先生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.45,0:21:50.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么也没做...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.78,0:21:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不光什么都没做?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.10,0:21:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把小猫带回来还给大家添了莫大的麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.61,0:22:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是...都是我让大家十分担心和为难
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.66,0:22:09.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛...人人为我我为人人 这就是生活啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.34,0:22:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.44,0:22:15.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你注意到送走小猫后千帆和千世的伤感
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.61,0:22:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为她们唱了歌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.51,0:22:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只想把老奶奶和小宝宝的事告诉她们而已
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.26,0:22:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那份心意让她们觉得放心了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.50,0:22:29.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来歌声也可以治愈心灵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.04,0:22:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过啊...我耳朵上的伤口治愈不了啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.19,0:22:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 这次小鸠你是零分
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.45,0:22:44.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不过圆圆的 好像今天的月亮姐姐一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.03,0:22:46.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高兴个屁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.48,0:22:49.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这么说来牛奶的盘子也是圆圆的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.16,0:22:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是圆圆的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.82,0:22:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 那么喜欢圆圆的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.87,0:22:55.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后就都是零分吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.48,0:22:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?太过分了 五百祗先生

Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.19,0:24:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}[...夏日的记忆.]

Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.98,0:23:07.62,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}人はみな飛んでみたいのに
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.79,0:23:15.05,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}重力に騙されてるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.24,0:23:23.15,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}誰もほんとは飛べるんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.30,0:23:32.19,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}あの子があんなに悲しそうなのは
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.57,0:23:42.55,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}自分の影をどこかに忘れてきちゃったからかも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.85,0:23:45.16,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}それなら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.48,0:23:49.51,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}ありがとうって　君に言えたら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.68,0:23:53.51,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}ありがとうって　君が笑えば
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.71,0:24:00.90,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}いったりきたり　嬉しくなる
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.27,0:24:05.65,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}君が幸せになる
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.88,0:24:10.07,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}心配なんていらないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.24,0:24:14.46,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}一緒にいるから
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.94,0:24:27.24,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}嬉しくても涙が出るなんて不思議だ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.98,0:23:07.62,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}明明人们都是那么想飞翔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.79,0:23:15.05,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}只不过被重力所欺骗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.24,0:23:23.15,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}其实谁都可以在天上翱翔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.30,0:23:32.19,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}那个孩子为什么如此悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.57,0:23:42.55,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}也许是把自己的影子忘在了哪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.85,0:23:45.16,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}是那样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.48,0:23:49.51,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}如果能对你说 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.68,0:23:53.51,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}如果能看见你的笑容 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.71,0:24:00.90,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}来来往往中 变得愉悦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.27,0:24:05.65,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}你一定能变得幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.88,0:24:10.07,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}不需要担心
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.24,0:24:14.46,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}因为我们在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.94,0:24:27.24,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}喜极而泣总是那么不可思议
